OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Name
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A non-unique identifier for a record/document often used as a search tool.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: A more descriptive identifier (that does need to be unique) of a record/document that is used as a default search option along with the search key (that is unique and mostly shorter). It is up to 60 characters in length.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Warehouse
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The location where products arrive to or are sent from.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: The Warehouse identifies a unique Warehouse where products are stored or Services are provided.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DEFAULT_EXPRESSION: if (OB.getWindowId() != "183" && OB.getWindowId() != "167") { if (OB.getWindowId() && OB.getSession().getAttribute(OB.getWindowId() +"|M_WAREHOUSE_ID")) { OB.getSession().getAttribute(OB.getWindowId() +"|M_WAREHOUSE_ID"); } else { if (OB.getContext().getWarehouse() != null) { OB.getContext().getWarehouse().id; } } }

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: UOM
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A non monetary unit of measure.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: The UOM defines a unique non monetary unit of measure

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Standard Price
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The regular or normal price of a product in the respective price list.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: The Standard Price indicates the standard or normal price for a product on this price list

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Business Partner Category
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A classification of business partners based on defined similarities.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: A way of grouping business partners together for classification and reporting purposes. Provides a method of defining certain defaults to be used when opening new business partners.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Product
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: An item produced by a process.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: Identifies an item which is either purchased or sold in this organization.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Generic Product
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: Generic product related to this product. The product will inherit all the properties defined in the generic product. Such as taxes or price.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Price Limit
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The lowest net price a specified item may be sold for.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: The Net Price Limit indicates the lowest price for a product stated in the Price List Currency.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Characteristic Description
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: Text with the concatenation of the characteristics and its values assigned to the product.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Search Key
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A fast method for finding a particular record.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP:
A search key allows for a fast method of finding a particular record. If you leave the search key empty, the system automatically creates a numeric number originating from a document sequence defined in the "Document Sequence" window. The sequence naming convention follows a rule "DocumentNo_TableName", where TableName is the actual name of the database table (e.g. C_Order).
Usually, company's internal identifiers for various records (products, customers, etc) are stored here.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Price List Version
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A price list with a specified validity range.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: Each Price List can have multiple versions. The most common use is to indicate the dates that a Price List is valid for.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: List Price
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The official net price of a product in a specified currency.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: The Net List Price is the official price stated by the selected pricelist and the currency of the document.

OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.NAME: Currency
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.DESCRIPTION: An accepted medium of monetary exchange that may vary across countries.
OBUISEL_SELECTOR_FIELD.HELP: Indicates the currency to be used when processing this document.
